<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>bitcandy - 온라인 커뮤니티</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Pretendard:wght@400;600;700;900&display=swap');
        body { font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif; background-color: #f3f4f6; color: #1f2937; }
        .page { display: none; }
        .active { display: block; }
        .btn-gray { background-color: #374151; color: white; transition: 0.2s; }
        .btn-gray:hover { background-color: #111827; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200 sticky top-0 z-50 shadow-sm">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 h-16 flex justify-between items-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tighter cursor-pointer" onclick="showPage('main')">
                <span class="text-gray-900">bit</span><span class="text-gray-400">candy</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
                <button onclick="showPage('login')" class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500">로그인</button>
                <button onclick="showPage('register')" class="btn-gray px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold">회원가입</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
        <section id="main" class="page active">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-8">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">비트캔디 보드</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 mt-1">함께 만들어가는 깨끗한 소통 공간입니다.</p>
                </div>
                <button onclick="showPage('write')" class="btn-gray px-6 py-2.5 rounded-xl font-bold">글쓰기</button>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl divide-y divide-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="p-6 hover:bg-gray-50 cursor-pointer flex gap-6" onclick="showPage('postDetail')">
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-gray-400 w-8">
                        <button class="hover:text-gray-900">▲</button>
                        <span class="text-sm font-black text-gray-700 my-1">10</span>
                        <button class="hover:text-gray-900">▼</button>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">비트캔디 커뮤니티에 오신 것을 환영합니다.</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">자유롭게 게시글을 남겨주세요.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="py-20 text-center text-gray-400 text-sm italic">"새로운 게시글이 아직 없습니다."</div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="postDetail" class="page">
            <button onclick="showPage('main')" class="mb-6 text-sm font-bold text-gray-400">← 목록으로</button>
            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-md flex gap-8">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3">
                    <button class="text-gray-300 hover:text-gray-900 text-xl font-bold">▲</button>
                    <span class="font-black text-gray-800 text-lg">10</span>
                    <button class="text-gray-300 hover:text-gray-900 text-xl font-bold">▼</button>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">비트캔디 커뮤니티에 오신 것을 환영합니다.</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-lg mb-10">환영합니다. 본 사이트는 깃허브 배포를 위해 최적화된 초기 버전입니다.</p>
                    <div class="border-t pt-8">
                        <h3 class="font-bold mb-4 uppercase text-xs tracking-widest text-gray-500">Comments</h3>
                        <textarea class="w-full p-4 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl text-sm mb-2" placeholder="댓글을 남겨주세요."></textarea>
                        <div class="flex justify-end"><button class="btn-gray px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold">등록</button></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="write" class="page">
            <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-8">새로운 글 작성</h2>
                <input type="text" placeholder="제목" class="w-full px-5 py-4 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl mb-4 focus:outline-none">
                <textarea rows="10" placeholder="내용을 입력하세요" class="w-full px-5 py-4 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl mb-6 focus:outline-none resize-none"></textarea>
                <div class="flex gap-4">
                    <button onclick="showPage('main')" class="flex-1 font-bold text-gray-400">취소</button>
                    <button onclick="showPage('main')" class="flex-[2] btn-gray py-4 rounded-xl font-bold shadow-lg">등록하기</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="login" class="page">
            <div class="max-w-sm mx-auto bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-10 mt-10 shadow-xl text-center">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-10">bitcandy</h2>
                <input type="text" placeholder="ID" class="w-full px-5 py-3.5 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl mb-4">
                <input type="password" placeholder="Password" class="w-full px-5 py-3.5 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl mb-6">
                <button class="w-full btn-gray py-4 rounded-xl font-bold shadow-md">Login</button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <script>
        function showPage(pageId) {
            document.querySelectorAll('.page').forEach(p => p.classList.remove('active'));
            document.getElementById(pageId).classList.add('active');
            window.scrollTo(0, 0);
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>

